      "The derived bounds may be too conservative, leading to suboptimal performance.",
      "The framework may not scale well to very large models or datasets.",
      "The proposed approach may require significant computational resources for training and validation."
    ]
  }
}
```

This refined proposal addresses the gap in the literature by focusing on the application of PAC-Bayes theory to latency-aware inference systems, providing a novel and impactful research direction. The experiments are designed to validate the proposed framework and demonstrate its effectiveness compared to existing approaches. The potential risks and limitations are also outlined to ensure a comprehensive evaluation of the proposal.
