        "Description": "Compare LASS with static pruning and heuristic skipping methods on WILDS benchmarks to assess robustness under distribution shifts.",
        "Metrics": "Accuracy Retention, Latency Variance"
      },
      {
        "Description": "Measure the impact of LASS on hidden state perturbation and spectral stability diagnostics across different layers.",
