', 'Experiment 2: Assess scalability on language models (BERT, GPT-2) using GLUE benchmarks. Metrics: Latency, Perplexity, Hidden-state perturbation.', 'Experiment 3: Compare against heuristic layer-skipping methods (e.g., HiLoRA) on domain generalization tasks. Metrics: Inference time, Accuracy, Parameter efficiency.'], 'Risk Factors and Limitations': ['Risk 1: Spectral stability bounds may not generalize across all architectures, limiting applicability.', 'Risk 2: Dynamic threshold adjustment could introduce computational overhead, offsetting latency gains.', 'Limitation: The method assumes access to layer-wise Jacobian computations, which may not be feasible in all deployment settings.']}
